    • Uses of AtomicModelFactoryI in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models

      Classes in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.hioa.models that implement AtomicModelFactoryI 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractAtomicHIOA_Factory
      The class AbstractAtomicHIOA_Factory implements the basic functionalities of atomic HIOA factories.
      class  StandardAtomicHIOA_Factory
      The class StandardAtomicHIOA_Factory defines a basic factory used when the instantiation protocol of an atomic HIOA model class does not modify the one defined in the class AtomicHIOA.
      class  StandardRTAtomicHIOA_Factory
      The class StandardRTAtomicHIOA_Factory defines a basic factory used when the instantiation protocol of a real time atomic HIOA model class does not modify the one defined in the class AtomicHIOA.

    • Uses of AtomicModelFactoryI in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models

      Classes in fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models that implement AtomicModelFactoryI 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractAtomicModelFactory
      The abstract class AbstractAtomicModelFactory provides the basic implementation for atomic model factories.
      class  StandardAtomicModelFactory
      The class StandardAtomicModelFactory defines an atomic model factory that will create models from their Java representation class, assuming that this model class declares a constructor with the three standard parameters: the URI of the model, the simulation time unit and the simulation engine.
      class  StandardRTAtomicModelFactory
      The class StandardRTAtomicModelFactory implements the standard model factory for real time atomic models.
